data.description: COME VISIT THIS CHARMING 4 BDRM 2.5 BA 2 Story home in the Point of Rocks Estates Subdivision in Chesterfield County. This home features a Living room w/C/FAN & LVP flooring throughout, kitchen w/ plenty of wood cabinetry, LAM C/TOP, bar w/butcher block C/TOP, EIK area and pantry. The laundry room, 1/2 bath & access to ATT garage complete the 1st floor of the home.  The 2nd floor features a PRIM BR, w/NEW carpet, ATT bath w/ tub/shower combo & single vanity w/ storage. Continue down the hall to find 3 additional bedrooms w/ NEW carpet, C/FANs & ample closet space, a shared hall bath, linen closet & pull down attic storage complete the space. This home boasts LVP throughout 1st level and NEW carpet upstairs, attached garage, 12X11 back deck and fenced in backyard great for pets or entertaining family and friends.  This home is a MUST SEE! Schedule your tour today.
